      • Book

        public Book(Author author,
            Date published,
            java.lang.String title)
        Non-default constructor for objects of class Book. Assumes the prior existence of all components, but each may optionally be null.
        Parameters:
        author - person who wrote the book; null defaults to "A. Non Ymous"
        published - date of publication; null defaults to whatever the default Date is
        title - primary identification of the book that appears on the cover; null is replaced with a default
